800x695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fpipocamoderna.com.br%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fsupergirl-2-800x695.jpg&h=eca792e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卡娜當上女超人不久，負責緝拿外星逃犯的政府秘密部門「超自然行動局」（DEO）突然前來干預，並從他們口中得知，當年被自己母親緝捕的各種危險的外星罪犯，其所關押的氪星監獄「羅茲堡」意外伴隨她的宇宙船一起被送到地球上。部分囚犯逃出後開始潛藏在世界各個角落、作惡多端，裏面的罪犯甚至包括一些來自氪星的激進分子。因此，卡娜設法與作戰部合作緝捕這些罪犯時，同時也得面對地球上的危險分子，化身為「女超人」來為世界與國際城證明自己的存在價值<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f30f2267\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=FjfXLVNGf54Mqq3HKCvM3bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=453658da\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab012fac80c5cd1462babfec17f8f2065299946","tid":805573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758e2d84a548531c5ce78ab4ed3cadb2bfe0395a","tid":805573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c2f7df24bc7c75744dc6895f656a4b358c153f","tid":805573,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"